@startuml
title Сценарий с ошибкой: Сбой уведомления и Retry

skinparam Style strictuml

actor "Датчик (Sensor)" as Sensor
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Processing Service" as ProcSvc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Event Bus" as Bus
participant "Notification Worker" as Worker
participant "Telegram API" as TG

== Регистрация критического показания ==

Sensor -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/readings\n{sensor_id: "T-101", value: 35.0}
activate Gateway
Gateway -> ProcSvc: Пересылка
activate ProcSvc

ProcSvc -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
activate DB
ProcSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO readings...
DB --> ProcSvc: OK
ProcSvc -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
DB --> ProcSvc: Committed
deactivate DB

note over ProcSvc #FFAAAA: 35.0 > 30.0! ТРЕБУЕТСЯ АЛЕРТ

ProcSvc -> Bus: publish(AlertTriggered)
activate Bus
Bus --> ProcSvc: ACK
deactivate Bus

ProcSvc --> Gateway: 201 Created
deactivate ProcSvc
Gateway --> Sensor: 201 Created
deactivate Gateway

== Асинхронная обработка (Сбой) ==

Bus -> Worker: consume(AlertTriggered)
activate Worker

Worker -> TG: sendMessage("Критический перегрев!")
activate TG
note over TG #FFAAAA: Connection Timeout (Service Down)
TG --x Worker: Error / Timeout
deactivate TG

note over Worker: Стратегия: Сохранить в очередь на повтор

Worker -> DB: INSERT INTO notification_retry\n(alert_id, status='pending', next_run=NOW()+1m)
activate DB
DB --> Worker: OK
deactivate DB
deactivate Worker

== Повторная попытка (через 1 минуту) ==

... 1 минута спустя ...

note over Worker: Фоновый процесс (Scheduler)\nзапускает попытку повторно

Worker -> DB: SELECT * FROM notification_retry WHERE status='pending'
activate Worker
activate DB
DB --> Worker: 1 запись найденa
deactivate DB

Worker -> TG: sendMessage("Критический перегрев!")
activate TG
TG --> Worker: 200 OK
deactivate TG

Worker -> DB: UPDATE notification_retry SET status='sent'
activate DB
DB --> Worker: OK
deactivate DB
deactivate Worker

@enduml